data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom all-brick home with 2-car garage, spanning 2,057 square feet in SE Springfield. Inside you'll find recessed ceilings, natural light, and beautiful hardwood floors, carpet and ceramic tile throughout. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and a functional island. The Master bedroom has plenty of room and features a master bathroom with double vanity sinks, a jetted tub, and walk in shower. All bedrooms including the master have spacious walk-in closets. Relax & entertain on the covered back deck overlooking the large privacy-fenced backyard or cozy up for the night by the wood-burning fireplace in the living room. This home offers modern comforts, a quiet neighborhood, walking trails close by, and a great space for your family. As an added bonus, this home does have the option for the buyer to assume the existing FHA loan!
